title: Quick Take: New York Primary Results
description: Hillary Clinton and Donald Trump won the night in Tuesday's New York state primary. Details on the results — and what's next in the race — with campaign reporters Sam Sanders and Scott Detrow and political editor Domenico Montanaro. Email the show at nprpolitics@npr.org. More coverage at nprpolitics.org.
